{"type": "article", "id": 20007, "title": "荧光灯组", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-31T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000932bYAzWvaKQqoEIyTG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦的设计师 Rachel Harding 用荧光灯做了一系列图形设计，荧光灯排成圆形，十字架形等特殊的图案，罩在玻璃后面，通过玻璃的折射，能在开灯后产生特别的彩虹效果。设计师认为荧光灯是生活中最常见的一种，但依然有它的图形感和简单的美。<a href=\"http://www.rachelharding.co.uk/vase-1/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150324cyZhNdGqEMkfQl96.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150324VoCaZqe2ycujhFOT.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150325uKbRJ3h246P8fzVC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150325dJmrhQWG0lnxB5SM.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}